Titolo: Gal Gun

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: Gal Gun is a Japanese bishōjo rail shooter game developed by Inti Creates and published by Alchemist. It was first released on Xbox 360 in 2011, followed by a PlayStation 3 port a year later. The game takes place in a fictional academy in Japan, where the player takes the role of a male student, Tenzou Motesugi. He must shoot his female classmates, who are running desperately after him, with "Pheromone Arrows" to prevent them from making their partner, while he finds one of the four lead girls before sunset.
A remastered version, titled Gal Gun Returns, was released in Japan and Asia for Nintendo Switch on January 28, 2021, and in North America and Europe on February 12. A Microsoft Windows version was also released worldwide on the same date.

Genere: Bishōjo 

Valutazione: 62
